WEBVTT

1
01:18:49.640 --> 01:18:50.800 
他们朝着你去了
They're coming at you.

2
01:18:52.640 --> 01:18:53.800 
收到
Copy that.

3
01:18:55.120 --> 01:18:57.000 
等等 他们要困住我们
Wait, wait. See? They're trying to trap us.

4
01:18:57.080 --> 01:18:58.320 
漂移到紧急停车带上去
Here, just drift onto the shoulder.

5
01:18:58.400 --> 01:18:59.560 
不 我要冲着悍马过去
No, no, no, I'm going for the Hummer.

6
01:19:00.040 --> 01:19:01.400 
他只是个虚张声势的衰货
He's a pavement prowler.

7
01:19:01.480 --> 01:19:02.520 
什么衰货
Pavement what?

8
01:19:02.600 --> 01:19:04.960 
那是辆大幅改高车身的臭显摆车
It's a show car with a big lift kit.

9
01:19:05.040 --> 01:19:07.480 
为了掩盖驾驶者的自卑情绪
It makes up for his inferiority complex.

10
01:19:12.840 --> 01:19:13.840 
等等 你疯了吗
Wait. Are you crazy?

11
01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:17.730 
怎么 等一下
Wait, wait! Whoa, whoa!

